{"tid":1146574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高登好波! 牙joe派華為手機益大家!!!","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T10:17:02.000Z","uid":161892,"like":21,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a25c4deb3dabdd8abcfb2710113be109eb415d34","tid":1146574,"uid":161892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/09/152646_6a0781b0d2c607b48ee02366384d1b86.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F09%2F152646_6a0781b0d2c607b48ee02366384d1b86.jpeg&h=bc5375ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由17直播Live、metroX主辦，《都市日報》、《八八通》、Club SIM、熊仔頭藍仔頭、高登討論區跨平台合作，舉辦首個破格網絡紅人主播選舉「17都市驚喜」，17位入圍的候選主播已經亮相，大家可以投票支持心水主播。至於投票選出「17都市驚喜」主播的觀眾，即有機會得到華為Mate 20 Pro手機一部。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=28731&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmobile%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D28731%26catid%3D35&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=83929c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=28731&amp;catid=35</a><br />\n<br />\n各位ching快d去投票拎華為手機<br />\n估唔到牙joe咁為我地著想!!! 連土豪手機都肯送<br />\n呢d野無得賺 只求打個和<br />\n係時候回家g持牙joe爸爸😭"},{"pid":"7ffbe3a07daad29d0be8a6058282e85b88497a99","tid":1146574,"uid":31186,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"P30 都出先送P20"},{"pid":"aecddd03d69ca00176c375e08f694f324a580a24","tid":1146574,"uid":150685,"like":162,"dislike":1,"score":161,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dki2fQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDki2fQn.jpg&h=5ddd9e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飲東江水，用華為電話，高登生活態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d145b8222f12ebf114cf0a6f080ae7588d0c7b7","tid":1146574,"uid":3241,"like":